        <mxCell id="seq-summary-text" value="1. Script calls ingest_reference_data(tickers=['AAPL', 'MSFT'])&lt;br&gt;2. For each ticker: Rate limit -> HTTP GET -> API JSON response&lt;br&gt;3. Facet transformation: normalize() -> postprocess() -> validate()&lt;br&gt;4. BronzeSink writes Parquet with partitions (snapshot_dt, asset_type)&lt;br&gt;5. Result: storage/bronze/securities_reference/snapshot_dt=2024-11-21/asset_type=stocks/" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Courier New" vertex="1" parent="1">
